						               													<description>The obstacle of housing shortage has been plaguing the government for a long time. Finally, the government has made an important decision: handing over several plots of land to large investors and contractors to build high towers! After many challenges, 3 large plots of land have finally been selected in 3 different neighborhoods of the city to build 5 towers on each by the biggest investors of the city.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Build &amp;amp; Blast, players are given the role of the investors, to build 5 towers in a neighborhood each round, and while doing so, secretly invest in some towers. To earn more points, players should try to raise the tower on which they have invested more and sabotage other towers. The game ends at the end of the third round with the construction of 5 towers in the third neighborhood, and the investor with the most points will win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Build &amp;amp; Blast, there are several tiles, each representing a floor of a tower. In each neighborhood, 5 towers with 5 different designs and colors will be built. Some tiles belong to one or two specific towers, and some tiles can be placed in the body of all towers. A few special tiles, without being inserted into the body of the towers, will make changes to the building plans.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
